<view class="page review-rules">
  <block wx:if="{{status === 'loading'}}">
    <view class="page-content review-rules__pad">
      <ui-skeleton rows="{{6}}" title="{{true}}" />
    </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:elif="{{status === 'error'}}">
    <view class="page-content">
      <ui-empty
        title="无法加载规则"
        description="{{errorMessage}}"
        actionText="重试"
        bind:action="onRetry"
      />
    </view>
  </block>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="page-content review-rules__body">
      <ui-card shadow="{{true}}" padding="{{true}}">
        <text class="review-rules__title text-h2">评价奖励规则</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">
          平台鼓励用户提交真实、有效的服务评价，用于提升门店与服务透明度。奖励与好评、差评无直接绑定关系。
        </text>
        <view class="review-rules__notice">
          <ui-compliance-notice type="reward" />
        </view>
        <text class="review-rules__section text-h3">发放原则</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">1. 订单真实完成且评价通过平台审核；</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">2. 不要求必须 5 星或修改差评；</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">3. 售后中、退款中订单奖励可冻结；</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">4. 命中风控的评价不发放奖励；</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">5. MVP 阶段奖励为 mock 记录，正式金额以运营配置为准。</text>
        <text class="review-rules__section text-h3">禁止行为</text>
        <text class="review-rules__para text-body">不得出现「好评返现」「晒图返现」等诱导好评行为；商家不得私下返现换好评。</text>
      </ui-card>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
